---
title: Creamy Mushroom and Chicken Alfredo with Linguine and Spinach
description: Perfect pasta doesn't take a lot of ingredients or time! This creamy chicken Alfredo has a secret ingredient: soy sauce! Adding soy sauce to the mushrooms gives this Alfredo an umami kick.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/linguines-alfredo-cremeuses-aux-champignons-et-au-poulet-4d3f033e.jpg
